neutral, filt, mean, pw = pd.DataFrame(columns=header), pd.DataFrame(columns=header), pd.DataFrame(columns=header), pd.DataFrame(columns=header)
for folder in os.listdir('./emergeant_neutrality'):
    if os.path.isdir('./emergeant_neutrality/'+folder):
        text_file = open('./emergeant_neutrality/'+folder+"/is_neutral.txt", "r")
        results = text_file.read().split('\n')
        typ = results[-1]
        typ = typ.split('\t')
        typint = []
        for i in range(len(typ)):
            try:
                typint += [float(typ[i])]
            except:
                typint += [typ[i]]
        results = results[:-2]
        results = np.array([[int(j) for j in i.split('\t')] for i in results]).T
        results = results.tolist()
        for i,t in enumerate(typint):
            results += [t]
        d = {header[i]:results[i] for i in range(len(header))}
        res = pd.Series(d, name=str(folder))
        if d["generation"]-100<1:
            if d["community_assembly_model"]=='neutral':
                neutral = neutral.append(res)
            elif d["community_assembly_model"]=='filtering':
                filt = filt.append(res)
            elif d["community_assembly_model"]=='competition':
                mean = mean.append(res)
            else:
                pw = pw.append(res)

neutral_y = np.mean([neutral["is_neutral"].values[i] for i in range(len(neutral))], axis = 0)

pw_y = np.mean([pw["is_neutral"].values[i] for i in range(len(pw))], axis = 0)

plt.plot(mean_y[1:], color="#FB6542", label="mean")

plt.legend()
plt.show()
In [106]:
neutral500, filt500, mean500, pw500 = pd.DataFrame(columns=header), pd.DataFrame(columns=header), pd.DataFrame(columns=header), pd.DataFrame(columns=header)
for folder in os.listdir('./emergeant_neutrality500'):
    if os.path.isdir('./emergeant_neutrality500/'+folder):
        text_file = open('./emergeant_neutrality500/'+folder+"/is_neutral.txt", "r")
        results = text_file.read().split('\n')
        typ = results[-1]
        typ = typ.split('\t')
        typint = []
        for i in range(len(typ)):
            try:
                typint += [float(typ[i])]
            except:
                typint += [typ[i]]
        results = results[:-2]
        results = np.array([[int(j) for j in i.split('\t')] for i in results]).T
        results = results.tolist()
        for i,t in enumerate(typint):
            results += [t]
        d = {header[i]:results[i] for i in range(len(header))}
        res = pd.Series(d, name=str(folder))
        if d["generation"]-500<1:
            if d["community_assembly_model"]=='neutral':
                neutral500 = neutral500.append(res)
            elif d["community_assembly_model"]=='filtering':
                filt500 = filt500.append(res)
            elif d["community_assembly_model"]=='competition':
                mean500 = mean500.append(res)
            else:
                pw500 = pw500.append(res)

for i in range(len(pw500)):
    if pw500["ecological_strength"][i]<0.004:
        pw1 += [pw500["is_neutral"][i]]
    elif pw500["ecological_strength"][i]<0.04:
        pw2 += [pw500["is_neutral"][i]]
    elif pw500["ecological_strength"][i]<0.4:
        pw3 += [pw500["is_neutral"][i]]
    elif pw500["ecological_strength"][i]<2:
        pw4 += [pw500["is_neutral"][i]]
    else:
        pw5 += [pw500["is_neutral"][i]]
